ms within the MSSM. Also, it is compatible with thermal leptogenesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2016 18:59:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 17:25:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 12 Dec 2017 15:14:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-13"}
